---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Legal Notice | WinFlowz";
---

<MainLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  lang="en"
  structuredData={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "@id": "https://winflowz.com/legal",
    "url": "https://winflowz.com/legal",
    "name": "Legal Notice | WinFlowz",
    "description": "Legal information and mandatory notices for WinFlowz digital productivity tools and services.",
    "inLanguage": "en"
  }}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Legal Notice</h1>

    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Last updated: December 15, 2024</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">1. Legal Information</h2>
      <p>This website and associated services are operated by:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Company Name: WinFlowz</li>
        <li>Owner: Diane Defores</li>
        <li>Address: 4 Quai Juin 40, Loire Aution 49250, France</li>
        <li>Email: contact@winflowz.com</li>
        <li>Business Activity: Digital Productivity Tools and Services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">2. Professional Activity</h2>
      <p>
        WinFlowz specializes in developing and providing digital productivity tools and services, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Software development and distribution</li>
        <li>Productivity training and consulting</li>
        <li>Digital workflow optimization</li>
        <li>Windows productivity enhancement tools</li>
        <li>Professional development services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">3. Hosting Information</h2>
      <p>This website is hosted by:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Provider: Vercel Inc.</li>
        <li>Address: 340 S Lemon Ave #4133, Walnut, CA 91789, USA</li>
        <li>Website: https://vercel.com</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">4. Authentication Services</h2>
      <p>User authentication is provided by:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Provider: Supabase</li>
        <li>Website: https://supabase.com</li>
        <li>Data Processing: Compliant with GDPR regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All content and materials available on this website and associated products are the property of WinFlowz, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Software and source code</li>
        <li>Training materials and documentation</li>
        <li>Brand elements and visual identity</li>
        <li>Product names and descriptions</li>
        <li>Website content and structure</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">6. Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data processing complies with:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)</li>
        <li>French Data Protection Act</li>
        <li>Applicable international privacy laws</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">7. Professional Insurance</h2>
      <p>
        Professional liability coverage includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Professional indemnity insurance</li>
        <li>Business liability coverage</li>
        <li>Digital services protection</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">8. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>
        In case of disputes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>French law applies to all transactions and services</li>
        <li>Courts of Loire Aution have jurisdiction</li>
        <li>Mediation is available for consumer disputes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">9. Business Registration</h2>
      <p>
        Business details:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Registration: French Business Registry</li>
        <li>VAT Registration: Non applicable</li>
        <li>Business Structure: Individual Enterprise</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-8">
        This legal notice may be updated periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes through our website or email communications.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
      For any legal inquiries, please contact legal@winflowz.com
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
